<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.2.10">
<l>veṉṟiviṭai yuṭaṉēḻaṭart tavaṭikaḷai</l>
<l>maṉṟilmalipukaḻ maṅkaimaṉ kalikaṉṟicol</l>
<l>oṉṟuniṉṟavoṉ patumuraippavar taṅkaḷmēl</l>
<l>eṉṟunillā viṉaiyoṉṟuñ collilulakilē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>On those who say the nine [verses] with one remaining,</l>
<l>The words of Kalikaṉṟi, king of Maṅkai, whose fame abounds in assemblies,</l>
<l>About the deity who victoriously conquered seven bulls at once,</l>
<l>Not any evil fate will ever endure; if [one] speaks [truly],</l>
<l rend="indent">[nor] on the whole world.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
